cat=auto
desc=This staff can cast the CharmPerson and CharmMonster spells, and can grant a power equivalent to a ControlPlant potion. Each function uses one charge. A newly created staff has 30 charges; a staff found in a treasure hoard will have 3d10 charges remaining.

[StaffofHealing]
