desc=This wand generates a 40' conical blast of cold doing 6d8 damage (save vs. Magic Wands for half). Wands can only be used by arcane spellcasting classes. A newly created wand has 20 charges, and each use of the wand depletes one of those charges; a wand found in a treasure hoard will have 2d10 charges remaining.

[WandofEnemyDetection]
weight=0.5
type=wand
cat=auto
desc=The effect of this wand is to make all enemies of the user within 60' glow with a greenish-white light for one round. Even hidden or invisible enemies glow in this way, revealing them, but enemies completely out of sight (such as behind a wall) may not be seen by the user. An "enemy" is any creature which is hostile to the user, including undead and constructs.

